item.title: Pi damn errors! help me
item.dc:creator: @The_Outsider The Outsider
item.description:
@The_Outsider wrote:

If it cannot find the symbol then either:

-It does not exist.
-You spelled it wrong (case sensitive).
-You didn’t import.

Look carefully at what you’re trying to do and see what’s wrong, or use an IDE.
